Package com.ts8t.objects

Class Link

java.lang.Object
com.ts8t.objects.Link
public class Link extends Object
Author:
Rob Kempf

A Link is the base distance component of a roads on an AreaMap. It is a vector with one begin Node and one end Node, and is a straight approximation of a road segment in a single direction. A two-way road is represented by two links pointed in opposite directions. A Link is also used to define one step in a Route.
